{"type":null,"faqId":12306,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00） 个别图片分辨率小于720P，在手机端打开时，不能全屏显示，不能放大","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">目前在</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">EMUI2.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">上图片的放大是按照图片本身大小线性变化的，会对比手机的分辨率和图片的分辨率进行计算。优化之前部分图片默认放大后显示不清晰</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">这张图片的分辨率是</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">282X500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">，手机分辨率是</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">720P</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">，图片长宽都不到手机屏幕的</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">1/2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">，这个时候图片会被”默认“放大到两倍显示，不会超过全屏</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">所以会看到这张图片默认是按照图片的</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\">倍显示的，但是不能放大，只能缩小到图片原始尺寸。</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:black;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":13,"unUseful":7,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3124","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1399273272000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":4079,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"5","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":